INSTRUCTIONS

The program frequency.py will give you the frequency of occurence of a each word in a block of text.

step 1 - Paste the block of text that has to processed into the file "input.txt"
step 2 - Open a terminal window and open the directory "text_processor"
step 3 - Enter the below command into the terminal window

		" python3 frequency.py input.txt"

Once these steps are excecuted the terminal window will display the frequency of each word in the block text
The result of this program will be written onto file called "input.txt.out" in the same directory
